<div id="main-content" class="mt-[75px] p-4 sm:mt-0 sm:w-3/4 bg-gray-50 mx-auto">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">方敏英阿美語字典 - 附錄</h1>

    <!-- 文件資訊說明 -->
    <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 rounded">
      <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
        <p>附錄1. 阿美語的文法要素</p>
        <p class="ml-4">首尾接辭</p>
        <p class="ml-4">重複接辭</p>
        <p class="ml-4">文法上的連接詞</p>
        <p class="ml-4">代名詞</p>
        <p>APPENDIX 1. GRAMMATICAL COMPONENTS IN THE AMIS LANGUAGE</p>

        <!-- 使用 details 標籤實現展開/收合 -->
        <details class="mt-2 toggle-details">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-semibold list-none flex items-center gap-1">
            <span class="when-closed">展開完整內容</span>
            <span class="when-open hidden">收起完整內容</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 arrow-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </summary>

          <p class="ml-4">AFFIXES</p>
          <p class="ml-4">REDUPLICATION</p>
          <p class="ml-4">Connective Grammatical Markers</p>
          <p class="ml-4">PRONOUNS</p>
          <p>附錄 2. 文法上的用法－應用範例</p>
          <p>APPENDIX 2. GRAMMATICAL USAGE - PARADIGMS</p>
          <p>衍生語言單字表</p>
          <p>DIALECT WORD LISTS</p>
          <p class="ml-4">花蓮衍生語言單字及意義</p>
          <p class="ml-4">HUALIEN DIALECT WORD LIST</p>
          <p class="ml-4">光復衍生語言單字及意義</p>
          <p class="ml-4">KWANGFU DIALECT WORD LIST</p>
          <p class="ml-4">南方衍生語言單字及意義</p>
          <p class="ml-4">SOUTHERN DIALECT WORD LIST</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PDF 顯示區域 -->
    <div class="mt-6">
      <div class="border border-gray-300 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-gray-100">
        <object
          data="<%= "/files/方敏英阿美語字典-附錄.pdf" %>#toolbar=1&navpanes=1&scrollbar=1"
          type="application/pdf"
          class="w-full h-[800px] sm:h-[900px]">
          <!-- 如果瀏覽器不支援 object 標籤，顯示替代內容 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full p-8">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-gray-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V9.414a1 1 0 00-.293-.707l-5.414-5.414A1 1 0 0012.586 3H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">您的瀏覽器無法顯示 PDF 檔案</p>
            <%= link_to "點擊此處下載 PDF",
                        "/files/方敏英阿美語字典-附錄.pdf",
                        class: "px-6 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-lg",
                        target: "_blank" %>
          </div>
        </object>
      </div>

      <!-- 下載按鈕 -->
      <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center gap-4">
        <%= link_to "/files/方敏英阿美語字典-附錄.pdf",
                    class: "inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md transition duration-200",
                    target: "_blank" do %>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
          </svg>
          在新視窗開啟
        <% end %>

        <%= link_to "/files/方敏英阿美語字典-附錄.pdf",
                    class: "inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md transition duration-200",
                    download: true do %>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path>
          </svg>
          下載 PDF
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
